{
  "texts": [
    "In her words: I am not sure if I could be who I am elsewhere.",
    "I mean, I have a relationship with the territory.",
    "In this case, if I have a relationship with the mountains, with the channels to which I carry out ceremonies.",
    "I am not sure if I could go somewhere else to do that.",
    "So I surely depend on this territory … So it is surely unthinkable for us to not live here."
  ]
}